channel.title: TwistedFate Development
channel.description:
[center]-Reserved-[/center]
[b]Introduction[/b] Hello, welcome to the development thread for TwistedFate. This thread is dedicated to not only introduce the name but to obtain some helping hands in allowing our progress to become quicker so we can achieve our ultimate goal! We strive to make a professional atmosphere with respectful members of our staff team in which we want to achieve the best out-standing RSPS out there.
[b]Background-Information[/b] This server has opened not too long ago, it's been open for about three days, and the server being the popular Project-Insanity(P.I.) that has been founded by Cody. Even though this is the most used source out there, we strive to make sure that it's the most unique one out there and plan on adding our own personal touches to it.
The server and forums itself are there for us to give us some experience, and further improve our programming skills one way or another.
[b]Development Team[/b] Client Development:
[ul][li]Cody[/li][/ul]
Server Development
[ul][li]Cody[/li][/ul]
Website Development:
[ul][li]Soulcist (James)[/li][/ul]
[b]Application Format[/b]
[code] Profession: (server/client/web/graphics) Portfolio: (provide some of your past/current work) Reason: (tell me why you would like to be a part of this team) Personal: (tell me some things about yourself, such as your favorite hobbies, music, etc.) [/code]
[b]Update Log[/b]
[code]The update log will be kept here, and updated when time has been given to do-so.[/code]
[b]Media[/b]
- Reserved -
Thank You,
James TwistedFate Administration Team
